# Title: Invoke-Obfuscation COMPRESS OBFUSCATION - PowerShell
# Author: Timur Zinniatullin, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-18
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects Obfuscated Powershell via COMPRESS OBFUSCATION
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1027, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/powershell/powershell_script/posh_ps_invoke_obfuscation_via_compress.yml

ScriptBlockText IN ("*system.io.compression.deflatestream*", "*system.io.streamreader*") ScriptBlockText="*new-object*" ScriptBlockText="*text.encoding]::ascii*" ScriptBlockText="*readtoend"